1 in 7 Americans are food insecure. We want to help end hunger. We need your help. Shop at the Grocery store you love. Jenerus let's you choose which grocery store is your food bank.

The Jenerus Extension allows you to easily sync your online grocery store shopping cart with your Jenerus account. When your shopping cart is funded, easily check out with the money from Jenerus and the Jenerus Extension.

For more information visit http://jenerus.com.
